<HEAD>
<TITLE>Laser Diagnostics as a Tool for Visualization of Flame Propagation and Emissions</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY Background="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Hintergrund.GIF" >
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Publik/Projects/index.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Balken-UP.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=100%  BORDER=0  ALT="IET/LVV ETHZ UP"></A>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>Laser Diagnostics as a Tool for Visualization of Flame Propagation and Emissions</FONT>
<P>
<HR WIDTH=100%  ALIGN=CENTER SIZE=3>
<P>
<B>
Summary:
</B>
<P>
The knowledge of the main chemical reactions and the physical conditions associated with the process offers the opportunity for developing theoretical models of combustion phenomena. The success of this modelling is dependent on the possibility of accurate measurements of a number of combustion species in various environments. The objective is to develop a method of studying flame fronts in engines under homogeneous charge conditions and the study of turbulence effects on the combustion process. The general principle of flame front detection is based on the visualization of a species which is strongly affected by the flame. This can be achieved by adding small quantities of tracer molecules which are excited by laser light. Laser Induced Fluorescence (LIF) imaging techniques will be used to map species concentrations. In addition Mie and Raman scattering will be employed to obtain the time-resolved flame structure.
<P>
A spectral approach for modelling flame front-turbulence interactions runs in parallel with the experiments.
<P>
Contacts:
<P>
T. Steiner, B. Ineichen, K. Boulouchos
<P>
Electronic Contacts:
<P>
<A HREF="mailto:"steiner@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch>steiner@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch</A>
<P>
Index Terms:
<P>
Optical Flame Visualization<BR>
Time-Resolved Flame Structure<BR>
Species Detection
<P>
Supported By:
<P>
National Energy Research Fund (NEFF) Grant Number NEFF 597.
<P>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Home_Public.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="Home Page Public"></A>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Intern/Erste_Seite_Intern.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Home_Intern.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="Home Page Intern"></A>
<A HREF="mailto:www@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Administrator.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="e-mail to administrator"></A>
<P>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Publik/Projects/index.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Balken-DOWN.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=100% BORDER=0  ALT="IET/LVV ETHZ DOWN"></A>
