<HEAD>
<TITLE>Transition to Turbulence in Complex Geometry Flows</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY Background="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Hintergrund.GIF" >
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Publik/Projects/index.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Balken-UP.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=100% BORDER=0  ALT="IET/LVV ETHZ UP"></A>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>Transition to Turbulence in Complex Geometry Flows</FONT>
<P>
<HR WIDTH=100%  ALIGN=CENTER SIZE=3>
<P>
<B>Summary:
</B>
<P>
In the past two decades there has been significant progress in our understanding of transition to turbulence, especially in simple geometry flows, such as plane channel flows, open shear flows and boundary layers. Recent advances in high-order numerical methods and computers make the use of Direct Numerical Simulation feasible for complex geometry flows. In this project we focus on separated flows in channels with sudden expansions (backward-facing step, symmetric sudden expansion). In particular,
 two-dimensional simulations are performed using a Spectral-Element method, while the three-dimensional simulations are based on a
Spectral-Element/Fourier method. Systematic studies of classification of instabilities and transition to turbulence are performed. Computational results are in good agreement with experimental data.
<P>
Contacts:
<P>
L. Kaiktsis
<P>
Electronic Contacts:
<P>
<A HREF="mailto:"kaiktsis@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch>kaiktsis@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch</A>   
<P>
Index Terms:
<P>
Computational Fluid Dynamics<BR>
Direct Numerical Simulation<BR>
<P>
Supported By:
<P>
Swiss Federal Office of Energy (BEW), Grant Number EF-FOS (88)6.
<P>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Home_Public.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="Home Page Public"></A>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Intern/Erste_Seite_Intern.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Home_Intern.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="Home Page Intern"></A>
<A HREF="mailto:www@lvv.iet.mavt.ethz.ch"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Administrator.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=33% BORDER=0  ALT="e-mail to administrator"></A>
<P>
<A HREF="http://troja.ethz.ch/Publik/Projects/index.html"><IMG  SRC="http://troja.ethz.ch/Seiten_Ausstattung/Balken-DOWN.GIF" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=100% BORDER=0  ALT="IET/LVV ETHZ DOWN"></A>
