<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>My Interests</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="overiver.gif">
<BR>
<B>My Spare Time Activities</B> <BR>
<BR>
<B><EM>Reading</EM></B><BR>
<BR>
This is my main activity. I realy enjoy english novels, especially crime stories of the Victorian age. My favorite authors are:
<UL>
<LI>Anne Perry
<LI>Elizabeth George 
<LI>The Bront&eumls</UL>
And here a few Comics, which I read very frequently:<BR>  
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://infolabwww.kub.nl:2080/calvin_hobbes/">Calvin and Hobbes</A>
<LI>Asterix and Obelix
<LI>The Adventures of Tintin
<LI>Theodor Pussel</UL>
<P><CENTER><HR WIDTH="80%" ALIGN="CENTER" SIZE="4"></CENTER>
<BR>
<B><EM>Listening to Music</EM></B><BR> 
<BR>
My favorite musicians are:
<UL>
<LI>Alison Moyet (Yazoo)
<LI>Stevie Nicks
<LI>Kenny G
<LI>Jean Jacques Goldman
</UL>
<P><CENTER><HR WIDTH="80%" ALIGN="CENTER" SIZE="4"></CENTER>
<BR>
<B><EM>Sport</EM></B><BR>
<BR>
I'm very interested in any kind of sport. I often go <A HREF="http://econ-www.newcastle.edu.au:80/~bill/billspor.html">cycling</A>, and once a week I play a game of badminton and squash. From time to time I go jogging.<BR>
<P><CENTER><HR WIDTH="80%" ALIGN="CENTER" SIZE="4"></CENTER>
<BR>
<B><EM>Travelling</EM></B><BR>
<BR>
Any time I have the money and time, I travel to other countries and try to become
acquainted with the culture of their natives. The best days I ever had, were on a trip
from Pitsburgh to Cincinatti on the amazing <A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/TheTropics/3127/tallstkb.html">Delta Queen</A>.<BR>
<P><CENTER><HR WIDTH="80%" ALIGN="CENTER" SIZE="4"></CENTER>
<BR>
<B><EM>Parlor Games</EM></B><BR>
<BR>
I play parlor games whenever I meet with friends. The most entertaining games are:
<UL>
<LI>The Settlers of Catan
<LI>Ligretto
<LI>Carrom
</UL>
<P><CENTER><HR WIDTH="80%" ALIGN="CENTER" SIZE="4"></CENTER>
<BR>
<EM>Last update: 12-Jan-97, Author: Rolf Pfiffner</EM> 
</BODY>
</HTML>
